{"text": " Exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly and empty yourself of air before For you inhale, inhale easily onto your empty body, exhale from the top, from the chest, Just pull the belly in to push out the air, allow your body to inhale easily into internal Emptiness, again vertical exhalation from the top, from the chest, from the belly. Pull the belly inward and push out the air from the body. On the next exhale down, bring your mind lower into your torso. With the exhale, bring your attention towards your abdominal area. with each exhale bring your mind and connect with the lower abdomen towards the area of the belly. Exhale, and reach lower towards the darkness of the bell. Reach and connect with the center of gravity. Pull the belly in, a little more, push out the air and connect with the center. From thought, to the center of gravity, let go of any breathing, just stay in the the center. If thought comes in, exhale from the belly and connect with the center of gravity.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 4.379999999999999, "end": 20.66, "text": " Exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly and empty yourself of air before", "tokens": [50364, 31911, 490, 264, 6690, 11, 490, 264, 7443, 11, 490, 264, 11696, 293, 6707, 1803, 295, 1988, 949, 51400], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2189320217479359, "compression_ratio": 1.1805555555555556, "no_speech_prob": 0.06819546222686768, "words": [{"word": " Exhale", "start": 4.379999999999999, "end": 5.779999999999999, "probability": 0.4977053701877594}, {"word": " from", "start": 5.779999999999999, "end": 7.18, "probability": 0.8151261210441589}, {"word": " the", "start": 7.18, "end": 7.36, "probability": 0.9929908514022827}, {"word": " nose,", "start": 7.36, "end": 7.8, "probability": 0.9890735745429993}, {"word": " from", "start": 8.88, "end": 10.56, "probability": 0.9712018966674805}, {"word": " the", "start": 10.56, "end": 10.72, "probability": 0.9963988065719604}, {"word": " c